                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 17.967,
                                "byte_start": 76800,
                                "byte_stop": 148689,
                                "text": "The disposition in 73-190, Bellis against the United States; 73-726, Cooper against Kopke; 72-1382, Rich against the United Stated will be announced by Mr. Justice Marshall."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 17.967,
                        "stop": 122.164,
